    "The reason is that an item is a piece of data that can be as small as a token or as big as a whole document.",
    "As above, choosing which mechanism to use will depend on the desired guarantees and runtime.",
    "Finally, we cover alignment issues, which include discrimination, the generation of toxic, harmful, or hateful outputs, and the unlearning of unwanted capabilities.",
    "Regarding methods that focus on fairness or the mitigation of biases and discrimination, our survey has revealed that most studies focus on gender discrimination related to pronouns (e.g., \"doctor\" is more frequently associated with \"him\" while \"nurse\" is more frequently associated with \"her\").",
    "While addressing this issue is crucial, we believe it represents a limited perspective on bias, which in fact manifests across many more dimensions."
